_sText:
A fun prefab I was going to use in my hosties map
but since I'm to busy to finish the map ...
I give u guys the prefab called : Find the Geek
New game for Hosties map ^^
How to play :
1 T and 1 CT on the circles 
Of each team a teammate has to enter a cube .
And start guessing ONE AT A TIME . Just shoot the brush and it opens the cube 
When A T finds the CT in one of his cubes in front of him he may kill the CT
Same way for CT

Simple but fun :)
